----------------------------------------
TINYLDBG
----------------------------------------

A tiny lua debugger that is loaded into a lua runtime and helps with diagnostics, circa 2006.

----------------------------------------
NOTES
----------------------------------------

Simply hook/call tinyldb.start() from a command line environment.

Requires lua debug module.

---------------------------------------
FUNCTIONALITY
---------------------------------------

start/reset/shutdown/help

breakpoints
 - creating
 - removing
 - saving
 - loading
 - displaying
 - clearing
 - enabling
 - disabling

stepping
 - 1 or more lines
 - over
 - continue

dumping
 - callstack
 - globals
 - upvals
 - locals
 - function environment
 - function info
 - variabls by name

setting
 - variables by name
 - copying variables

executing raw lua
